OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a "greatly
OL,7,Frespected" South Wales Police officer
OL,8,Fwhose body was discovered in Bristol
OL,9,Fcity centre's harbour.
OL,11,FPC Reehan Akhtar, 28, from Llanelli
OL,12,Fwas on a night out with friends in the
OL,13,Fcity over the weekend. He became
OL,14,Fsubject to a missing persons' search
OL,15,Fafter being last seen in the early
OL,16,Fhours of Sunday.
