OL,6,FOn Monday, Avon and Somerset Police
OL,7,Fconfirmed that a body was recovered
OL,8,Ffrom the water during their searches
OL,9,Fand that PC Akhtar's family had been
OL,10,Foffered support by a specialist family
OL,11,Fliaison officer.
OL,13,FOn the same day, the police force said
OL,14,Fthey were treating his death as
OL,15,Funexplained, but not suspicious, and
OL,16,Fwill be preparing a file for the
OL,17,Fcoroner.
