OL,6,FSouth Wales Police has now issued its
OL,7,Fown tribute to him saying that "it is
OL,8,Fwith immense sadness that we confirm
OL,9,Fthe news of the passing of our
OL,10,Fcolleague and friend PC 8650 Rehaan
OL,11,FAkhtar."
OL,13,FPC Akhtar started his police career
OL,14,Fwith South Wales Police in 2021 as a
OL,15,FPCSO in Cardiff. He then went on to
OL,16,Ftrain as a Police Officer and in
OL,17,FSeptember 2023 went to join the local
OL,18,Fteam in Swansea as a Police Constable.
