OL,6,FSouth Wales Police's Chief Constable
OL,7,FJeremy Vaughan said: "I was shocked
OL,8,Fand saddened to learn of Rehaan's
OL,9,Fpassing.
OL,11,F"At this difficult time, our hearts go
OL,12,Fout to Rehaan's family and friends,
OL,13,Fand we will do all we can to support
OL,14,Fthem.
