OL,6,F"During his time with South Wales
OL,7,FPolice he served our communities with
OL,8,Fpride and professionalism as both a
OL,9,FPCSO and a Police Officer. I know he
OL,10,Fwas greatly respected and liked by his
OL,11,Fcolleagues and those he met as part of
OL,12,Fhis day-to-day duties.
OL,14,F"On behalf of South Wales Police, I
OL,15,Foffer our heartfelt condolences to all
OL,16,Fof those impacted by his passing."
OL,18,FLlanelli-based Calsonic Kansei Swiss
OL,19,FValley who PC Akhtar played football
OL,20,Ffor have also issued their own tribute
OL,21,Fto him on social media.
