OL,6,F"It is with great sadness that we
OL,7,Fshare the devastating news of the
OL,8,Fpassing of Rehaan Akhtar.
OL,10,F"Rehaan was a committed 1st Team
OL,11,Fplayer, a passionate footballer, and a
OL,12,Fvalued presence both on and off the
OL,13,Fpitch. He was a friend to many, known
OL,14,Ffor his positivity, determination, and
OL,15,Flove for the game.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts and heartfelt
OL,18,Fcondolences are with Rehaan's family,
OL,19,Ffriends and all who knew him during
OL,20,Fthis difficult time.
